Reasoning: The paper discusses the use of massive MIMO techniques in wireless communication networks and proposes a novel system design using an electromagnetic lens to reduce hardware and signal processing costs while improving performance. This topic falls under the intersection of several computer science sub-disciplines, including information theory (cs.IT), networking and internet architecture (cs.NI), systems and control (cs.SY), multimedia (cs.MM), and physics (cs.PHYS).
